":0},"title":"Hadith on Sunan: Four raka&#8217;at of prayer before &#8216;Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray four cycles before afternoon prayer, separating them with the invocation of peace upon the favored angels and those who follow them among the Muslims and believers. Al-Tirmidhi said, \"Ibrahim ibn Ishaq preferred not to separate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/no-salat-asr-fajr-exceptions\/","url_meta":{"origin":12949,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer after \u2018Asr and Fajr, with exceptions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, only prayed two cycles after the afternoon prayer because some property came to him, which occupied him from performing two cycles after the noon prayer. The Prophet prayed them after the afternoon prayer and he did not repeat it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/sunan-prayer-before-after-dhuhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":12949,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: The Prophet prays before or after","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, could not pray four cycles before noon prayer, he would pray them afterwards. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 426 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0639\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0638\u064f\u0651\u0647\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0647\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12941,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/for-rakaat-before-after-duhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":12949,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Four raka&#8217;at before, after Dhuhur prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Habibah reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Whoever preserves four cycles of prayer before noon prayer and after it, Allah will forbid him from entering the Hellfire.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 428 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0650\u0651 \u062d\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u062